creat group in ini_group of each target,

1 if add initiator name in ini_group, add lun in ini_group, then
	those initoators only can access those lun, if no lun, then those initiator can acces nothing
  note: you can use echo 'add ! xxxx' > mgmt to add all initiator except that one

2 even if the same disk is add to default target oriented lun dir, will not can be accessed
